---
import Boton from './Boton.astro';

const WSP_TEL = '51999888777';
const WSP_MSG =
  'Hola 👋 Quiero saber más sobre la asesoría en estrategia de VIBA Consultores.';
const wspHref = `https://wa.me/${WSP_TEL}?text=${encodeURIComponent(WSP_MSG)}`;

const estrella =
  'M12 1 Q13.4 10.6 23 12 Q13.4 13.4 12 23 Q10.6 13.4 1 12 Q10.6 10.6 12 1 Z';
---

<section
  id="inicio"
  class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-b from-champagne/25 to-transparent"
>
  <div
    class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl items-center gap-12 px-6 pb-24 pt-16 md:pt-20 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-10"
  >
    <div class="max-w-xl">

      <h1
        class="revelar font-serif text-4xl font-semibold leading-[1.08] text-charcoal sm:text-5xl lg:text-[3.4rem]"
        style="animation-delay: 80ms"
      >
        Estrategia que convierte tus ideas en <span
          class="relative whitespace-nowrap text-terracota"
          >resultados<svg
            class="absolute -bottom-1.5 left-0 h-2.5 w-full"
            viewBox="0 0 200 12"
            fill="none"
            preserveAspectRatio="none"
            aria-hidden="true"
            ><path
              d="M3 8C40 3 90 3 130 6c25 2 45 2 67-1"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="4"
              stroke-linecap="round"></path></svg
          ></span
        >.
      </h1>

      <p
        class="revelar mt-6 max-w-lg text-lg leading-relaxed text-charcoal/70"
        style="animation-delay: 160ms"
      >
        En VIBA Consultores ordenamos el rumbo de tu negocio, fortalecemos tu
        comunicación y te ayudamos a crecer con decisiones que sí funcionan.
      </p>

      <div
        class="revelar mt-8 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-center"
        style="animation-delay: 240ms"
      >
        <Boton variante="primario" href="#contacto">Quiero asesoría</Boton>
        <Boton variante="secundario" href={wspHref} target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          Escríbenos por WhatsApp
        </Boton>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div
      class="revelar relative mx-auto aspect-square w-full max-w-md lg:max-w-lg"
      style="animation-delay: 200ms"
    >
      <!-- Capa de fondo champán (profundidad) -->
      <div class="absolute right-0 top-2 h-[88%] w-[86%] rounded-[2.5rem] bg-champagne"></div>

      <!-- Arco salvia con monograma -->
      <div
        class="absolute inset-x-6 bottom-6 top-10 overflow-hidden rounded-t-full rounded-b-[2rem] bg-salvia"
      >
        <!-- Anillo brass interior -->
        <div class="absolute inset-5 rounded-t-full rounded-b-[1.5rem] border border-brass/50"></div>
        <!-- Monograma -->
        <span
          class="absolute inset-0 grid place-items-center font-serif text-[9rem] font-semibold leading-none text-crema/90"
        >
          VB
        </span>
      </div>

      <!-- Detalle brass -->
      <div class="absolute left-3 top-8 size-3 rounded-full bg-brass"></div>

      <!-- Sello terracota (arriba-derecha) -->
      <div
        class="absolute -right-2 top-0 grid size-24 place-items-center rounded-full bg-terracota text-crema shadow-[0_16px_30px_-12px_rgba(178,107,82,0.7)] ring-4 ring-crema"
      >
        <svg class="size-9" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d={estrella}></path>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <!-- Tarjeta flotante (abajo-izquierda) -->
      <div
        class="absolute -left-3 bottom-4 flex items-center gap-3 rounded-2xl border border-taupe/40 bg-marfil px-4 py-3 shadow-[0_18px_36px_-18px_rgba(44,49,53,0.4)]"
      >
        <span
          class="grid size-9 place-items-center rounded-full bg-charcoal font-serif text-sm font-semibold text-crema"
        >
          VB
        </span>
        <span class="text-sm font-medium leading-tight text-charcoal">
          Estrategia<br /><span class="text-charcoal/55">con propósito</span>
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
